## API Auth externa

> Esta API ya está implementada. No se modifica ni se replica.

### Endpoints

#### POST /api/auth/login
```json
// Request
{
  "usernameOrEmail": "admin",
  "password": "Admin123*"
}

// Response 200 OK
{
  "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
  "tokenType": "Bearer",
  "expiresIn": 3600,
  "user": {
    "userId": "5d9b1b80-7d65-4e07-9a16-0123456789ab",
    "email": "ana@universidad.edu",
    "role": "profesor"
  }
}

// Response 401 Unauthorized
{ "message": "Invalid credentials" }
```

#### POST /api/auth/register
```json
// Request
{
  "name": "Juan Perez",
  "email": "juan@universidad.edu",
  "password": "AnotherSecurePassword123*",
  "role": "estudiante"
}

// Response 201 Created
{
  "message": "User registered successfully",
  "user": {
    "userId": "f6d7c7c1-89d9-4f4e-aac2-abcdef123456",
    "email": "juan@universidad.edu",
    "role": "estudiante"
  }
}

// Response 409 Conflict
{ "message": "Email already exists" }
```

