## Checklist de pruebas manuales (PowerShell)

```powershell
$backend = "http://localhost:5000"
$tokenProfesor = "<JWT_PROFESOR>"
$tokenEstudiante = "<JWT_ESTUDIANTE>"

# GET público → debe retornar 200
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Get -Uri "$backend/api/collections"

# POST sin token → debe retornar 401
$body = @{ name = "Test"; description = "Test" } | ConvertTo-Json
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri "$backend/api/collections" -ContentType "application/json" -Body $body

# POST con estudiante → debe retornar 403
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri "$backend/api/collections" `
  -Headers @{ Authorization = "Bearer $tokenEstudiante" } `
  -ContentType "application/json" -Body $body

# POST con profesor → debe retornar 201
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri "$backend/api/collections" `
  -Headers @{ Authorization = "Bearer $tokenProfesor" } `
  -ContentType "application/json" -Body $body
```

